---

<ul>
  <li>
    <header>
      <small>portfolio</small>
      <h3>001 Archive</h3>
    </header>
    <p class='text_small'>Development portfolio and writing archive</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <header>
      <small>lab</small>
      <h3>002 Style</h3>
    </header>
    <p class='text_small'>Design, Animations, and 3D</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <header>
      <small>lab</small>
      <h3>003 Utility</h3>
    </header>
    <p class='text_small'>Utilities, Tools, and Jobs</p>
  </li>
